PROJECT PharmacyDispense
INTENT Prioritize medication dispensing orders and dispatch only when the priority score is high enough to warrant immediate action.
MODE risk
ENTITY Order

FIELDS Order
  urgency
  medication_risk
  stock_level
  patient_priority
  interaction_risk
  time_limit
END

GOAL maximize_safety
GOAL minimize_latency

CONSTRAINT risk > 0.75
ACTION_THRESHOLD 0.90

ACTION Dispense
  POLICY simulate_only
  CALL simulated.pharmacy.dispense
END
